name: Bauhaus Lithography Black
description:
Denne lithografi er trykt med sort sværte på 210 g. ubestrøget syrefrit papir.

Papiret har en offwhite tone.

Oplag: 40 stk.
Størrelse: 50x70 cm

Lithografiet er trykt som stentryk, og der findes kun ganske få steder i Danmark hvor man stadig anvender denne komplicerede trykmetode.

Prisen er uden ramme.

Motivet er en fortolkning af Bauhause stifteren Walter Gropius hus – dette er en bavlfacade.

-

This lithography is printed with black on 210 g. uncoated acid-free paper .

The paper has an off-white tone.

Edition: 40 pcs.
Size: 50x70 cm

Lithography printet on stone is an old technique, and there are only a few places in Denmark where you still can do this complicated printing method.

The price is borderless.

The subject is an interpretation of Bauhause founder Walter Gropius house - this is a hogwash facade.

name: Stilleben lithography

Motivet er en fortolkning af guldalder malernes stilleben opsætninger. Der står der "Reverse" i teksten under hovedet.

The paper has an off-white tone.

Edition: 24 pcs.
Size: 40 x 58 cm

Lithography printet on stone is an old technique, and there are only a few places in Denmark where you still can do this complicated printing method.

The price is borderless.

The subject is an interpretation of the Golden Age painters still life setups. It says that "Reverse" in the text below the head.
